# hey.  i tried to organize this to make it somewhat easier to read and
# locate things, but laziness and frustration are powerful enemies.
#
# there are three main categories: menus, osd, and windows
# each has four subcategories: colors, geometry, text, and textures
#
# i then tried to group the definitions together based on the objects
# or type of objects they modify but sometimes got lazy and just sorted
# them alphabetically (if i sorted them at all).
#
# feel free to copy this or whatever.  i don't care.




